snippet.title: Night Mission Pinball gameplay (PC Game, 1982)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Night Mission Pinball, Dos PC game produced by subLOGIC in 1982 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/night-mission-pinball/4201/
Playing a bit of pinball in this old-school military-themed game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
